Subject: [PATCH] ui: scaffold vertical tab sidebar WebUI panel

Registers the fennec://sidebar WebUI page and adds a sidebar SidePanel
entry to BrowserView. The sidebar hosts the React vertical tab list
(src/ui/sidebar/), workspace switcher, and pinned tabs.

The sidebar is rendered inside a SidePanel (Chromium's built-in right/
left side panel infrastructure) patched to support left-side positioning.

Design constraints:
  - Icon-only by default (48px wide): expands to 240px on hover
  - Ear motif: --fnc-sidebar-ear-accent-color stripe on the active tab
  - Pinned tabs anchor to the bottom of the list
  - Position (left/right) persisted per-profile as a pref

TODO: Stub. Full implementation in Phase 2.
